# Trade Signals

## Technical Indicators
### Trend Indicators
- Moving Average Crossover
  - Golden Cross (50/200 SMA)
  - Death Cross
- MACD Crossover
- Parabolic SAR Flip
- ADX Trend Strength (>25)

### Momentum Indicators
- RSI Signals
  - Oversold (<30)
  - Overbought (>70)
  - Divergence (Bullish/Bearish)
- Stochastic Crossover
  - %K/%D Cross
  - Overbought/Oversold
- CCI Extremes
  - >+100 (Overbought)
  - <-100 (Oversold)

### Volatility Indicators
- Bollinger Band Squeeze
- Band Breakout (Upper/Lower)
- ATR Spike
- IV Rank (>70th percentile)

## Chart Patterns
### Reversal Patterns
- Head & Shoulders
- Double Top / Double Bottom
- Triple Top / Triple Bottom
- Rounding Top / Bottom

### Continuation Patterns
- Flags (Bull/Bear)
- Pennants
- Triangles
  - Ascending
  - Descending
  - Symmetrical
- Cup & Handle

### Candlestick Patterns
- Bullish
  - Hammer
  - Bullish Engulfing
  - Morning Star
  - Piercing Line
- Bearish
  - Hanging Man
  - Bearish Engulfing
  - Evening Star
  - Shooting Star

## Price Action Signals
### Support & Resistance
- Breakout + Retest
- Bounce from S/R
- False Breakout

### Trend Signals
- Higher Highs/Higher Lows (Bull)
- Lower Highs/Lower Lows (Bear)
- Channel Break

### Volume Signals
- Volume Breakout
- Climax Volume
- Divergence (Price vs Volume)

## Fundamental Signals
### Earnings & News
- Earnings Beat/Miss
- Guidance Upgrade/Downgrade
- M&A Announcement
- Dividend Declaration

### Economic Data
- CPI / Inflation Data
- GDP Release
- Interest Rate Decision
- NFP / Employment Data

## Options-Specific Signals
### Option Chain Signals
- Max Pain Level
- PCR (Put-Call Ratio)
  - High PCR (>1.2) Bearish
  - Low PCR (<0.7) Bullish
- OI Buildup (Call/Put Walls)

### Greeks Signals
- High IV (Volatility Play)
- Theta Crush Setup
- Delta Neutral Entry

## Confirmation Signals
### Multi-Timeframe
- Daily Trend + 1H Entry
- Weekly Support + Daily Bounce

### Confluence
- MA + RSI + Volume
- Pattern + Indicator
- S/R + Candlestick

## Risk & Exit Signals
### Stop Signals
- Trendline Break
- MA Death (Price below key MA)
- Parabolic SAR Against

### Profit Signals
- Target 1/2/3 Hit
- RSI Divergence
- Trailing Stop Trigger
